    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood that is soft or easily cut, generally restricted to the timber of coniferous trees. Contrasted to "hardwood," which is usually, but not always, harder than softwood.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
